title: SCARLET 007 (2013) (Son of Ultron-Empire) BENDIS MALEEV
description:
Scarlet #7

Story by Brian Michael Bendis
Art by Alex Maleev
Cover by Alex Maleev
Publisher: Marvel Icon
Release Date: July 17th, 2013

The revolution is happening now. Scarlet takes city hall with her list of demands, and the city's reaction will surprise you.

The creator-owned hit of the year is back and bolder than ever! From the Eisner Award-winning team of Maleev and Bendis!
